#### Signature of the method ####

The name of the method.
check_todo

What parameters it takes, their names and data types.
string

What it returns and the data type of that value.
returns a boolean, true if string includes #TODO otherwise false

--------------------------------------------

#### Test examples ####

contains_todo = check_todo(string)

x if string is empty, throw an error
x if string includes todo returns false
x if string includes #todo returns false
